# ============================================================
# Synapse — repo-root environment variable index
# ============================================================
# There is no single repo-root .env. Configuration is split by component:
#
#   backend/.env.example   -> copy to backend/.env  (API + workers)
#   frontend/.env.example  -> copy to frontend/.env (Vite build-time vars)
#
# Copy the relevant template into a real `.env` in that directory and fill in
# real values. NEVER commit a real `.env` (all are gitignored).
#
# Key backend vars (see backend/.env.example for the full list):
#   DATABASE_URL, CHROMA_PERSIST_PATH, STORAGE_PATH, JWT_SECRET_KEY,
#   GROQ_API_KEY, GEMINI_API_KEY, ALLOWED_ORIGINS
#
# Key frontend var (create frontend/.env):
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api/v1
